title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Prime Cuts: Baker's Comps, Jets Mistake, Wentz's Surprise Return?
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Prime Cuts: Baker's Comps, Jets Mistake, Wentz's Surprise Return?
description:
The best of The Colin Cowherd Podcast. Colin rants on why Baker Mayfield is the Keanu Reeves of quarterbacks (0:44), why you can't blame the ownership for the Chargers move to LA (2:22), and why Carmelo Anthony is a terrible teammate (5:52). Colts Head Coach Frank Reich on why we might see Carson Wentz play Week 1, and the player that is unlike anybody he has ever been around before (7:17). John Middlekauff on why the Zach Wilson pick is already looking like a disaster for the Jets (16:40). Plus Rams GM Les Snead on why he loves trading 1st-round picks, and how Jared Goff actually helped bring Matt Stafford to LA (24:25). 

Make sure you follow Colin and The Volume on Twitter for the latest content and updates and check out FanDuel for the best wagering and daily fantasy action!
